    Paralysis open the vault, handed Darkmouse a food ration. He liked the 
little lady. She was cute, and according to Black Aracnia she would help them 
take the throne.
    "So, are you ready to see your commander? Black Aracnia told me to take 
you to him because your going to help us put Black Aracnia on the throne. And 
Quickstrike will be Sub-commander."
